{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Derpy Fish is a casual puzzle/adventure game where you guide a small school of fish. What you can do depends on how many fish are in your school. Have two, dash through pesky bubble streams. Have three, cut your way past ropes and grass. Have four, and gain the might to push boulders out of the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>A school is smart. Fish are dumb, panicky, derpy animals that couldn't find their way out of a goldfish bowl.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One misplaced step at the PetTrip has landed our fish friends in one of the many aquariums at the store, and now they need your help to escape. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A relaxing puzzle experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 different themed worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">7 unique school abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">64 puzzle levels to explore and solve</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3470090/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737594008","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3470090/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737594008","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3470090/35079fb3c6f5455c5abc149bc5f21cf7fe6e7f90/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737594008","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3470090/35079fb3c6f5455c5abc149bc5f21cf7fe6e7f90/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737594008","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Derpy Fish is a casual puzzle/adventure game where you guide a small school of fish. What you can do depends on how many fish are in your school. Have two, dash through pesky bubble streams. Have three, cut your way past ropes and grass. Have four, and gain